---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="FAQ | Auto Video">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <section class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>Do I need an account?</h3><p>No. You can access our platform and request early access instantly without creating an account.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Is the rendering in real-time?</h3><p>Auto Video uses advanced AI to generate video concepts, scripts, and scene planning. Output quality and speed depend on your specific project requirements.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Can I use it for ads and commercial content?</h3><p>Yes, Auto Video is designed for teams creating ads, explainers, storytelling reels, and other professional video content.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Where can I get support?</h3><p>Use the contact page to send us your requirements and timelines. Our team typically responds within 1-2 business days.</p></article>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
